    "Both humans and AI e.g., saw the symbols XYxx as an indication of transgender instead of a family with two boys since it was defined in the question that X represents a man and Y a woman.",
    "On average, the MLMs were able to answer 35.3% of questions correctly, which means just over a third.",
    "We therefore conclude that our dataset is challenging.",
    "The best performing model was Airoboros33B which scored 71.8% and therefore clearly above the reference LLM ChatGPT (60.9% correct answers) and even slightly above the human baseline.",
    "Some of the larger MLMs, especially the 30B parameter models were somewhat disappointing since they did not outperform their smaller siblings."
